==English==
===Transitive verb===
'''to devise'''
# to use the [[intellect]] to [[plan]] or [[design]] something
# to [[leave]] [[property]] in a [[will]]

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[keksiä]] (1), [[suunnitella]] (1), [[testamentata]] (2)

===Noun===
'''devise'''  (plural ''devises'')
# the act of leaving property in a will
# such a will, or a [[clause]] in such a will
# the property left in such a will
